    • Field Detail

      • A_FIELDS

        static final String A_FIELDS
        By default, all the fields are not returned during a GET request. You can use the _return_fields argument to get the desired data. You would have to explicitly mention the additional fields you require with a _return_fields+={requiredfield}. The following variables describe the fields for each record type. view and ttl fields are included by default as it's part of the base Record object.

        Note: AuthZone record doesn't have any TTL field.

        See Also:
